{"metadata":{"role":"article","title":"Github API","modules":[{"name":"App"}],"roleHeading":"Article"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App\/GithubAPI","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App\/ConfiguringSPM","doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App\/Architecture","doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App\/SpecificationSupport","doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App\/ToDoList"],"anchor":"Essentials"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/App\/documentation\/App"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/repos\/repos?apiVersion=2022-11-28#list-repository-tags","isActive":true}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/releases\/releases?apiVersion=2022-11-28#get-a-release-by-tag-name","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/repos\/contents?apiVersion=2022-11-28#get-repository-content","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/repos\/repos?apiVersion=2022-11-28#get-a-repository","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"},{"text":"List Repository Tags","type":"heading","anchor":"List-Repository-Tags","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/repos\/repos?apiVersion=2022-11-28#list-repository-tags","overridingTitle":"List Repository Tags","isActive":true,"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"List Repository Tags","type":"text"}]},{"text":" endpoint","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in the Github API provides a paginated list of tags for a repository:","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["$ curl -H \"X-GitHub-Api-Version: 2022-11-28\" \\","     -H \"Accept: application\/vnd.github+json\" \\","     -H \"Authorization: Bearer <your-PAT>\" \\","     --no-progress-meter \\","     https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/tags","[","  {","    \"name\": \"0.5.0\",","    \"zipball_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/zipball\/refs\/tags\/0.5.0\",","    \"tarball_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/tarball\/refs\/tags\/0.5.0\",","    \"commit\": {","      \"sha\": \"7977acd7597f413717058acc1e080731249a1d7e\",","      \"url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/commits\/7977acd7597f413717058acc1e080731249a1d7e\"","    },","    \"node_id\": \"MDM6UmVmMTI4NzkxMTcwOnJlZnMvdGFncy8wLjUuMA==\"","  },","  ...,","  {","    \"name\": \"0.1.0\",","    \"zipball_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/zipball\/refs\/tags\/0.1.0\",","    \"tarball_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/tarball\/refs\/tags\/0.1.0\",","    \"commit\": {","      \"sha\": \"b907805523ca75a0c9fdaaf1bdf81b3fe3360ac7\",","      \"url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/commits\/b907805523ca75a0c9fdaaf1bdf81b3fe3360ac7\"","    },","    \"node_id\": \"MDM6UmVmMTI4NzkxMTcwOnJlZnMvdGFncy8wLjEuMA==\"","  }","]"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Notice the information we need in each tag dictionary is: a) the tag "},{"code":"name","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"; and b) the "},{"code":"zipball_url","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which is an URL to download"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the source archive for that tag.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Tags vs Semantic Versions","level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Tags-vs-Semantic-Versions"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Notice that the tags listed above are simply git tags. They can be whatever the repository"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"author wants them to be: “1.2.3”, “v1.2.3”, “version_1.2.3”, or whatever."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/swiftlang\/swift-package-manager\/blob\/main\/Documentation\/PackageRegistry\/Registry.md#2-definitions","isActive":true},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the other hand, specifies that its versions MUST be semantic versions, as defined by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/semver.org\/"},{"type":"text","text":". This spec has a regular"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"expression associate with it which explicitly defines how a Semantic Version must"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"be parsed. That means that:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags like “1.2.3” ARE valid semantic versions; but","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags like “v1.2.3” or “version_1.2.3” are NOT.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This means that when we talk to the Github API, we must supply "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tags"}]},{"text":", but when we","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive requests and supply responses to the Swift Package Registry Service, then"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"we must provide "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"semantic versions","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For most repositories, this is not a problem - their tags ARE semantic versions. However,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for a few repositories which use tags like “v1.2.3”, we must provide the mapping between"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"semantic version and tag."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package Manager has to do this same thing. Therefore, we have tried to make our"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"logic for the tag <-> semantic version processing exactly the same as SPM. You can find"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"our processing of tags to semantic versions in "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/CrowdStrike\/swift-package-registry-service\/blob\/main\/Sources\/APIUtilities\/Version%2BTagMap.swift","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Get-A-Release-By-Tag-Name","text":"Get A Release By Tag Name"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As mentioned in the discussion of the List Repository Tags Github endpoint above,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the tag information contains the tag "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"name","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"zipball_url","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":". However,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when we respond to the Swift Package Registry Service Fetch Release Metadata endpoint","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GET \/{owner}\/{repo}\/{version}"},{"text":"), then there is an optional ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"publishedAt"},{"text":" date","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"which indicates when that release was published. That information is not available","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the List Repository Tags Github endpoint, since there may or may not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"a Github “release” associated with a particular tag.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However, if there IS a release associated with a tag, we can look up information about that release using the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Get A Release By Tag Name","type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/releases\/releases?apiVersion=2022-11-28#get-a-release-by-tag-name","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get A Release By Tag Name"}]},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"endpoint. That information includes when the release was published.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Here is an example of this endpoint:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["$ curl -H \"X-GitHub-Api-Version: 2022-11-28\" \\","       -H \"Accept: application\/vnd.github+json\" \\","       -H \"Authorization: Bearer <your-PAT>\" \\","       --no-progress-meter \\","       https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/releases\/tags\/0.5.0","{","  \"url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/releases\/16362611\",","  \"assets_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/releases\/16362611\/assets\",","  \"upload_url\": \"https:\/\/uploads.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/releases\/16362611\/assets{?name,label}\",","  \"html_url\": \"https:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/releases\/tag\/0.5.0\",","  \"id\": 16362611,","  \"author\": {","    \"login\": \"stephencelis\",","    \"id\": 658,","    \"node_id\": \"MDQ6VXNlcjY1OA==\",","    \"avatar_url\": \"https:\/\/avatars.githubusercontent.com\/u\/658?v=4\",","    \"gravatar_id\": \"\",","    \"url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\",","    \"html_url\": \"https:\/\/github.com\/stephencelis\",","    \"followers_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/followers\",","    \"following_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/following{\/other_user}\",","    \"gists_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/gists{\/gist_id}\",","    \"starred_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}\",","    \"subscriptions_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/subscriptions\",","    \"organizations_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/orgs\",","    \"repos_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/repos\",","    \"events_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/events{\/privacy}\",","    \"received_events_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/stephencelis\/received_events\",","    \"type\": \"User\",","    \"user_view_type\": \"public\",","    \"site_admin\": false","  },","  \"node_id\": \"MDc6UmVsZWFzZTE2MzYyNjEx\",","  \"tag_name\": \"0.5.0\",","  \"target_commitish\": \"master\",","  \"name\": \"The Boring Swift 5 Release\",","  \"draft\": false,","  \"prerelease\": false,","  \"created_at\": \"2019-03-26T15:19:07Z\",","  \"published_at\": \"2019-03-26T18:04:46Z\",","  \"assets\": [","","  ],","  \"tarball_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/tarball\/0.5.0\",","  \"zipball_url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/zipball\/0.5.0\",","  \"body\": \"### What's new?\\r\\n\\r\\n- Not much! We build for Swift 5 now!\"","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Notice the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"published_at"},{"type":"text","text":" field."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"So therefore, when we are responding to the Fetch Release Metadata endpoint,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"we will call this Github API endpoint to fetch the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"published_at"},{"type":"text","text":" field."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, given that there may not be a release associate with a specified tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"then this is not an error if this endpoint returns a ","type":"text"},{"code":"404 Not Found","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". In this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"case, we simply don’t provide the optional ","type":"text"},{"code":"publishedAt","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" field in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GET \/{owner}\/{repo}\/{version}"},{"text":" response.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Get-Repository-Content","text":"Get Repository Content","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In order to respond to the Swift Package Registry Service Fetch Manifest request","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(","type":"text"},{"code":"GET \/{owner}\/{repo}\/{version}\/Package.swift","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), then we have to:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Find the information about all the package manifests are present in the repository"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Normally there is always a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Package.swift"},{"text":", but there also could be Swift-version-specific","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"manifests, like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Package@swift-6.0.swift"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fetch the actual content of any of the package manifests"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We can do both of these things with the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get Repository Content"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.github.com\/en\/rest\/repos\/contents?apiVersion=2022-11-28#get-repository-content","type":"reference","isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"Get Repository Content"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"endpoint:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the path we supply in the request is a directory, then the response is a listing of all the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"files in that directory.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the path we supply in the request is a file, then the response is information about that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"file, including the Base64-encoded contents."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Here is an example of a directory request. Notice that the path after "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"contents\/"},{"type":"text","text":" and before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the query parameter ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"?ref=0.5.0"},{"type":"text","text":" is empty, meaning the root directory of the repository:"}]},{"code":["curl -H \"X-GitHub-Api-Version: 2022-11-28\" \\","     -H \"Accept: application\/vnd.github.object+json\" \\","     -H \"Authorization: Bearer <your-PAT>\" \\","     --no-progress-meter \\","     https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/contents\/?ref=0.5.0","{","  \"name\": \"\",","  \"path\": \"\",","  \"sha\": \"940f5b5642eab4df8dfce2c34450565cf3329350\",","  \"size\": 0,","  \"url\": \"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/pointfreeco\/swift-overture\/contents\/?ref=0.5.0\",","  \"html_url\": \"https:\/\/github.com